        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8459",
        "content": "A few sad tears does Betty shed.... She pats the pony, where or when She knows not.... happy Betty Foy! Oh, Johnny, never mind the doctor!'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
