        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8459",
        "content": "\"Now, we have no doubt this is all true: we will believe it, indeed we will, mr w Is it sympathy for the sheep you wish to excite?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
